{% doc %}
  @description Amount-based multi-milestone cart progress bar. Renders a
    templated unlock message, a horizontal track with evenly spaced milestone
    nodes (check state when reached), and an animated fill driven by the live
    cart total. Milestone data (thresholds, rewards) comes from
    spectrum_progress_campaign / spectrum_progress_milestone metaobjects;
    presentation comes from snippet props.

  @param c {object} Variant content object injected by the snippet wrapper.
    All keys optional — defaults below.
  @param c.campaign_handle {string} Handle of a spectrum_progress_campaign
    metaobject. Empty = first active campaign on the shop.
  @param c.bar_style {string} 'continuous' | 'segmented'
  @param c.marker_style {string} 'node_icon' | 'dot' | 'label_only'
  @param c.show_milestone_icons {boolean} Show per-milestone reward icons.
  @param c.bar_height {number} Track height in px.
  @param c.bar_corner {string} 'rounded' | 'square'
  @param c.show_labels {boolean} Show reward labels under nodes.
  @param c.pre_goal_template {string} Message before first milestone.
  @param c.mid_progress_template {string} Message between milestones.
  @param c.complete_message {string} Message when all milestones reached.
  @param c.message_alignment {string} 'left' | 'center' | 'right'
  @param c.show_check_on_reached {boolean} Check icon on reached nodes.
  @param c.show_confetti {boolean} Confetti burst on newly reached milestone.
  @param c.fill_animation {boolean} Animate fill width changes.
{% enddoc %}

{% comment %}
  Data contract: campaign config is read HERE in Liquid (server-side) because
  metaobjects are not available to cart.js. The resolved milestones are baked
  into the embedded JSON config; the asset JS only does cart math + DOM state
  updates on cart events. No app-proxy round trip.

  Eligible-scope caveat: cart.js line items carry no tags/collections, so only
  scope 'all' is computed client-side in v1. 'collection' / 'tag' scoped
  campaigns fall back to the full cart total (fields exist in the metaobject
  so scoped totals can land later without remodeling).

  Node positions are evenly spaced at index/(count+1) — matches the reference
  design (track extends past the last node) and stays stable however uneven
  the threshold amounts are. Fill interpolates linearly between node positions.

  Color pattern: theme tokens with the reference design's palette as
  fallbacks (light-blue card #e7f0fc, royal-blue fill #4b79dd, rest-track
  #c9daf3, deep-blue strong text #2f55a4).
{% endcomment %}

{% stylesheet %}
.sai-vg4guong {
  display: block;
  background: var(--sai-color-info-bg, #e7f0fc);
  border-radius: var(--sai-radius-card, 12px);
  padding: var(--sai-space-5, 1.4rem) var(--sai-space-4, 1rem) var(--sai-space-3, 0.75rem);
}
.sai-vg4guong__message {
  margin: 0 0 var(--sai-space-2, 0.5rem);
  font-family: var(--sai-font-heading, inherit);
  font-size: var(--sai-font-size-lg, 1.25rem);
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.35;
  color: var(--sai-color-info-text, #647eb5);
}
.sai-vg4guong__message strong { color: var(--sai-color-info-strong, #2f55a4); font-weight: 700; }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-align="center"] .sai-vg4guong__message { text-align: center; }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-align="right"] .sai-vg4guong__message { text-align: right; }

.sai-vg4guong__bar { position: relative; padding: 16px 0; }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-labels="on"] .sai-vg4guong__bar { margin-bottom: 3.1em; }
.sai-vg4guong__track {
  position: absolute; left: 0; right: 0; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
  height: var(--sai-vg4guong-bar-h, 5px);
  background: var(--sai-color-track, #c9daf3);
  border-radius: 999px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-corner="square"] .sai-vg4guong__track { border-radius: 0; }
.sai-vg4guong__fill {
  height: 100%; width: 0;
  background: var(--sai-color-accent, #4b79dd);
  border-radius: inherit;
}
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-anim="on"] .sai-vg4guong__fill { transition: width 0.45s ease; }

.sai-vg4guong__node-wrap {
  position: absolute; top: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}
.sai-vg4guong__node {
  width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  background: var(--sai-color-surface-raised, #ffffff);
  border: 2px solid var(--sai-color-track, #c9daf3);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--sai-color-info-bg, #e7f0fc);
  color: transparent;
}
.sai-vg4guong__node-wrap--reached .sai-vg4guong__node {
  background: var(--sai-color-accent, #4b79dd);
  border-color: var(--sai-color-surface-raised, #ffffff);
  color: var(--sai-color-surface-raised, #ffffff);
}
.sai-vg4guong__node svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; display: block; }
.sai-vg4guong__node img { width: 18px; height: 18px; display: block; object-fit: contain; }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-marker="dot"] .sai-vg4guong__node { width: 14px; height: 14px; }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-marker="dot"] .sai-vg4guong__node svg,
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-marker="dot"] .sai-vg4guong__node img { display: none; }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-marker="label_only"] .sai-vg4guong__node { display: none; }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-style="segmented"] .sai-vg4guong__node { box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px var(--sai-color-info-bg, #e7f0fc); }
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-checks="off"] .sai-vg4guong__node svg { display: none; }

.sai-vg4guong__label {
  position: absolute; top: calc(50% + 22px); left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
  /* Hard 110px cap + fixed-ish size: adjacent labels sit one node-gap apart,
     so anything wider than ~the gap collides at narrow widths. */
  width: 110px; max-width: 110px;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.25;
  color: var(--sai-color-text, #3a4456);
}
.sai-vg4guong[data-sai-labels="off"] .sai-vg4guong__label { display: none; }

.sai-vg4guong__node-wrap--pulse .sai-vg4guong__node { animation: sai-vg4guong-pulse 0.5s ease; }
@keyframes sai-vg4guong-pulse {
  0% { transform: scale(1); }
  50% { transform: scale(1.25); }
  100% { transform: scale(1); }
}
.sai-vg4guong__confetti {
  position: absolute; width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 2px;
  pointer-events: none;
  animation: sai-vg4guong-burst 0.9s ease-out forwards;
}
@keyframes sai-vg4guong-burst {
  0% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
  100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(var(--sai-vg4guong-cx, 0), var(--sai-vg4guong-cy, -60px)) rotate(320deg); }
}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .sai-vg4guong[data-sai-anim="on"] .sai-vg4guong__fill { transition: none; }
  .sai-vg4guong__node-wrap--pulse .sai-vg4guong__node { animation: none; }
  .sai-vg4guong__confetti { display: none; }
}
{% endstylesheet %}

{%- liquid
  assign campaign_handle = c.campaign_handle | default: ''
  assign bar_style = c.bar_style | default: 'continuous'
  assign marker_style = c.marker_style | default: 'node_icon'
  assign bar_height = c.bar_height | default: 5
  assign bar_corner = c.bar_corner | default: 'rounded'
  assign message_alignment = c.message_alignment | default: 'center'
  assign pre_goal_template = c.pre_goal_template | default: 'Add {remaining} more to unlock {reward}'
  assign mid_progress_template = c.mid_progress_template | default: "You're {remaining} away from {reward}"
  assign complete_message = c.complete_message | default: "Congrats! You've unlocked {reward} 🎉"

  if c.show_milestone_icons == nil
    assign show_milestone_icons = true
  else
    assign show_milestone_icons = c.show_milestone_icons
  endif
  if c.show_labels == nil
    assign show_labels = true
  else
    assign show_labels = c.show_labels
  endif
  if c.show_check_on_reached == nil
    assign show_check_on_reached = true
  else
    assign show_check_on_reached = c.show_check_on_reached
  endif
  if c.show_confetti == nil
    assign show_confetti = false
  else
    assign show_confetti = c.show_confetti
  endif
  if c.fill_animation == nil
    assign fill_animation = true
  else
    assign fill_animation = c.fill_animation
  endif

  assign campaign = nil
  if campaign_handle != blank
    assign campaign = shop.metaobjects['spectrum_progress_campaign'][campaign_handle]
  endif
  if campaign == nil
    for entry in shop.metaobjects['spectrum_progress_campaign'].values
      if campaign == nil and entry.active.value
        assign campaign = entry
      endif
    endfor
  endif

  assign milestones = nil
  if campaign
    assign milestones = campaign.milestones.value
  endif

  assign labels_attr = 'off'
  if show_labels
    assign labels_attr = 'on'
  endif
  assign checks_attr = 'on'
  unless show_check_on_reached
    assign checks_attr = 'off'
  endunless
  assign anim_attr = 'off'
  if fill_animation
    assign anim_attr = 'on'
  endif
-%}

{%- if milestones and milestones.size > 0 -%}
<div class="sai-vg4guong"
     data-sai-progress
     data-sai-style="{{ bar_style }}"
     data-sai-marker="{{ marker_style }}"
     data-sai-corner="{{ bar_corner }}"
     data-sai-align="{{ message_alignment }}"
     data-sai-labels="{{ labels_attr }}"
     data-sai-checks="{{ checks_attr }}"
     data-sai-anim="{{ anim_attr }}"
     style="--sai-vg4guong-bar-h: {{ bar_height }}px;">
  <script type="application/json" data-sai-progress-config>
{
  "milestones": [
    {%- for m in milestones -%}
    {%- liquid
      assign icon_url = ''
      if m.reward_icon.value
        assign icon_url = m.reward_icon.value.preview_image | image_url: width: 64
      endif
    -%}
    {"threshold": {{ m.threshold_amount.value | times: 100 | round }}, "label": {{ m.reward_label.value | json }}, "type": {{ m.reward_type.value | json }}, "code": {{ m.discount_code.value | json }}, "giftVariantId": {{ m.gift_variant.value.id | json }}, "icon": {{ icon_url | json }}}{%- unless forloop.last -%},{%- endunless -%}
    {%- endfor -%}
  ],
  "excludeDiscounted": {{ campaign.exclude_discounted_items.value | json }},
  "eligibleScope": {{ campaign.eligible_scope.value | json }},
  "preGoalTemplate": {{ pre_goal_template | json }},
  "midProgressTemplate": {{ mid_progress_template | json }},
  "completeMessage": {{ complete_message | json }},
  "showConfetti": {{ show_confetti | json }},
  "showMilestoneIcons": {{ show_milestone_icons | json }}
}
  </script>
  <p class="sai-vg4guong__message" data-sai-msg>&nbsp;</p>
  <div class="sai-vg4guong__bar" data-sai-bar>
    <div class="sai-vg4guong__track">
      <div class="sai-vg4guong__fill" data-sai-fill></div>
    </div>
    {%- assign denom = milestones.size | plus: 1 -%}
    {%- for m in milestones -%}
    {%- liquid
      assign pos = forloop.index | times: 100.0 | divided_by: denom
      assign icon_url = ''
      if show_milestone_icons and m.reward_icon.value
        assign icon_url = m.reward_icon.value.preview_image | image_url: width: 64
      endif
    -%}
    <div class="sai-vg4guong__node-wrap" data-sai-node data-sai-threshold="{{ m.threshold_amount.value | times: 100 | round }}" style="left: {{ pos }}%;">
      <div class="sai-vg4guong__node">
        {%- if icon_url != blank -%}
        <img src="{{ icon_url }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
        {%- else -%}
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
      <div class="sai-vg4guong__label">{{ m.reward_label.value }}</div>
    </div>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</div>
{%- endif -%}
